   "source": [
    "pd.crosstab(df['previous_loan_defaults_on_file'], df['loan_status'], normalize='index')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**Conclusion**:  \n",
    "\n",
    "Borrowers with a prior default history were observed to have fully repaid their loans in the dataset. This pattern appeared\n",
    "highly questionable and suggeted the possibility of **data leakage**.\n",
    "\n",
    "If such a feature was included in the model, borrowers with prior default records might be systematically classified as non-defaulters, leading to severe misclassification risk and potential financial losses for the bank.\n",
    "\n",
    "Therefore, this predictor would be excluded from the modelling process to prevent biased predictions. "
   ]
  },
