   "source": [
    "# Feature Screening"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "In this section, univariate logistic regression analyses were performed for numerical variables to assess their statistical significance in explaining the log-odds of default.\n",
    "\n",
    "For categorical variables, chi-squared tests of independence were conducted as an initial screening step to evaluate whether a significant association existed between each feature and the default outcome.\n",
    "\n",
    "As both statistical procedures required the default indicator (loan_status), this variable was preserved throughout the data partitioning process. "
   ]
  },
